name: Wet T-Shirt LORA
description:
Fun LORA for getting a wet white shirt. Pretty self-explanatory what it does, but the ideal weight for this in my experiments has been .07-.09.

Downside to this is that sometimes the wet shirt becomes liquid and I could not get it to do different colors than white for the shirt or smaller than H size boobs even though the training data has all these things.

trainedWords: <lora:wetshirt:.8> in a sheer see through wet white shirt
